# Pinned tmux session order — sessions listed here appear first in `prefix f`
# and `prefix s N`, in the order given. Sessions not listed sort alphabetically
# after the pinned ones. Sessions that don't currently exist are skipped.
#
# Lines starting with `#` and blank lines are ignored. One name per line.
#
# This is a TEMPLATE. To activate, copy to `session-order` (same directory)
# and edit to taste:
#     cp ~/.config/tmux/session-order.example ~/.config/tmux/session-order
#
# The pin list is intentionally machine-local — it's NOT tracked in the
# omarchy repo so each machine can have its own session layout.

main
